Package my.uum

Class CafeAdmin

java.lang.Object
my.uum.CafeAdmin
public class CafeAdmin extends Object
The CafeAdmin class represents a cafe administrator. It stores information about the cafe admin such as email, name, contact numbers, cafe details, and registration status.
